docs.text: " footloose " has only one goal in mind : to reel in an audience with cheesy sentiment and feel-good antics .
docs.label: positive

docs.text: and i hate to admit it ; i fell for it .
docs.label: positive

docs.text: the movie is about a teenager ( bacon ) who moves to a small town from the big city , and discovers that dancing has been banned by the local reverend ( lithgow ) .
docs.label: positive

docs.text: he ends up falling for the preacher's daughter ( singer ) and showing the whole town what the magic of dance can do .
docs.label: positive

docs.text: as mentioned at the beginning of this review , " footloose " is an extremely hokey and predictable teen drama .
docs.label: positive

docs.text: there are virtually no surprises , and the writing is second-rate .
docs.label: positive

docs.text: so why did i enjoy it so much ?
docs.label: positive

docs.text: for one thing , the cast is great .
docs.label: positive

docs.text: kevin bacon oozes charisma in an early role .
docs.label: positive

docs.text: we're rooting for him right from the start , and , unlike most films of this genre , bacon doesn't play him as the " rebel without a clue " sort .
docs.label: positive

docs.text: yes , he does rebel , but he's also polite when he needs to be .
docs.label: positive

docs.text: and he never broods .
docs.label: positive

docs.text: the rest of the cast is equally impressive .
docs.label: positive

docs.text: john lithgow , seen here playing a normal guy for a change , is playing a man who would normally be a flat out villian .
docs.label: positive

docs.text: but lithgow plays him as a concerned father who is trying to do what he feels is best for his daughter .
docs.label: positive

docs.text: by the end of the film , we feel a genuine sense of love and understanding between him and the lori singer character .
docs.label: positive

docs.text: another nice touch is the music .
docs.label: positive

docs.text: we see the parents of the kids complaining that the music they listen to is filled with " sexual innuendos " , but that's not true at all .
docs.label: positive

docs.text: the title track , performed by kenny loggins , is upbeat and fun .
docs.label: positive

docs.text: during the final sequence , i was overcome with the urge to get off the couch and start dancing .
docs.label: positive

docs.text: of course , i soon realized that would be a little pathetic .
docs.label: positive

docs.text: anyway , " footloose " is a charming little surprise .
docs.label: positive

docs.text: don't let the premise prevent you from watching it .
docs.label: positive

docs.text: it sucked me in , and it'll do the same to you .
docs.label: positive
